enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require a BaseProviders instance for generating ID numbers.
generateValid uses basePart to construct the base part of the ID number, which is crucial for setting up the test environment.
generateValid uses checksum to validate the generated ID number, making it essential for verifying the correctness of the generated ID number in tests.
firstDigit is used to determine the first digit of the ID number based on the birth year and gender, which is crucial for verifying the generated ID number in tests.
